landmarks.visual_description: A wide multi-lane asphalt road with yellow center line markings running horizontally across the bottom portion of the frame.

Several multi-story urban buildings with various architectural styles and orange-brown facades along the left edge of the frame.
A row of trees planted in the median dividing the main road, casting shadows on the pavement.
